OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1771945433
OL,3,CSEND, the disadvantage gap and
OL,4,Cattendance: What's in Labour's plan
OL,5,Cfor schools?
OL,7,FAfter months of delay, the government
OL,8,Fhas finally announced its long-awaited
OL,9,Fplan to reform the education system in
OL,10,FEngland.
OL,12,FThe proposed shake-up of special
OL,13,Feducation needs (SEND) support has
OL,14,Fdrawn significant attention, amid
OL,15,Fconcerns the reforms could trigger a
OL,16,Fbacklash from Labour backbenchers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1771945433
OL,3,CSEND, the disadvantage gap and
OL,4,Cattendance: What's in Labour's plan
OL,5,Cfor schools?
OL,7,FIn the Schools White Paper, published
OL,8,Fon Monday, the government announced it
OL,9,Fwould spend #4bn to make mainstream
OL,10,Fschools more inclusive for children
OL,11,Fwith SEND over the next three years.
OL,13,FBut the Schools White Paper is also
OL,14,Fpart of Labour's broader vision to
OL,15,Freform education - focusing heavily on
OL,16,Fdisadvantaged students, alongside
OL,17,Fplans to get missing children back to
OL,18,Fschool as absence rates have soared
OL,19,Fpost-pandemic.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1771945433
OL,3,CSEND, the disadvantage gap and
OL,4,Cattendance: What's in Labour's plan
OL,5,Cfor schools?
OL,7,FHere, ITV News has pulled together the
OL,8,Fkey proposals.
OL,10,FSpecial needs reform
OL,12,FThe key change announced on Monday is
OL,13,Fthat legal support plans, known as
OL,14,FECHPs, will be reserved for those with
OL,15,Fthe highest needs from 2035, meaning
OL,16,Faround one in eight children currently
OL,17,Freceiving the most support will move
OL,18,Fto new plans, according to government
OL,19,Festimates.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1771945433
OL,3,CSEND, the disadvantage gap and
OL,4,Cattendance: What's in Labour's plan
OL,5,Cfor schools?
OL,7,FInstead, new legally-binding documents
OL,8,Fcalled individual support plans (ISPs)
OL,9,Fwill be introduced, with multiple
OL,10,Flevels of support depending on the
OL,11,Fchild's needs.
OL,13,FThe government says there will be a
OL,14,Funiversal high quality of teaching for
OL,15,Fall children, with tiers of support
OL,16,Fcalled 'targeted', 'targeted plus',
OL,17,Fand 'specialist'.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1771945433
OL,3,CSEND, the disadvantage gap and
OL,4,Cattendance: What's in Labour's plan
OL,5,Cfor schools?
OL,7,FChildren classed as needing 'targeted'
OL,8,Fand 'targeted plus' support will have
OL,9,FISPs, and do not need a diagnosis.
OL,10,FOnly those who fall under the
OL,11,F'specialist' tier will be entitled to
OL,12,Fan EHCP.
OL,14,FThe government insists it will develop
OL,15,Fand build the new inclusive mainstream
OL,16,Fsystem over the next four years,
OL,17,Fbefore any children lose their EHCPs.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
