PN,31806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1771945433
OL,3,CSEND, the disadvantage gap and
OL,4,Cattendance: What's in Labour's plan
OL,5,Cfor schools?
OL,7,FThe number of children diagnosed with
OL,8,FSEND has rocketed in recent years,
OL,9,Falong with the number of children with
OL,10,FEHCPs, which has led to ballooning
OL,11,Fcosts for local authorities.
OL,13,FIn the last ten years, the amount
OL,14,Flocal councils spend on SEND has
OL,15,Falmost doubled from #7.8bn to a
OL,16,Fprojected #14.8bn for this year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1771945433
OL,3,CSEND, the disadvantage gap and
OL,4,Cattendance: What's in Labour's plan
OL,5,Cfor schools?
OL,7,FWhile councils struggle with huge
OL,8,Fbudget deficits driven by SEND,
OL,9,Ffamilies often face lengthy legal
OL,10,Fbattles to get their children the
OL,11,Fbasic level of support.
OL,13,FThe government says it is focused on
OL,14,Fimproving special needs support in
OL,15,Fmainstream schools, shifting away from
OL,16,Fthe current system, which has seen
OL,17,Frising numbers of children with SEND
OL,18,Fattending costly specialist schools.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1771945433
OL,3,CSEND, the disadvantage gap and
OL,4,Cattendance: What's in Labour's plan
OL,5,Cfor schools?
OL,7,FSpeaking on Monday, Education
OL,8,FSecretary Bridget Phillipson described
OL,9,Fthe SEND system as "broken", saying
OL,10,F"children's educations and lives have
OL,11,Fsuffered".
OL,13,FPhillipson said the level of support
OL,14,Fchildren receive will increase under
OL,15,Fthe plans: "Every child will get the
OL,16,Fbrilliant support they deserve, when
OL,17,Fthey need it, as routine and without a
OL,18,Ffight."
OL,26,@zD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
