PN,31809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1771945433
OL,3,CSEND, the disadvantage gap and
OL,4,Cattendance: What's in Labour's plan
OL,5,Cfor schools?
OL,7,FAfter 2029, the government says
OL,8,Fchildren will also be reassessed at
OL,9,Feach phase of school - that means
OL,10,Fpupils currently in year three or
OL,11,Fabove will keep their EHCP until at
OL,12,Fleast age 16, and those currently in
OL,13,Fyear two or below will be reassessed
OL,14,Fwhen they transition to year seven.
OL,16,FAs part of the plans, the government
OL,17,Fhas announced #1.6bn over three years
OL,18,Ffor early years settings, schools and
OL,19,Fcolleges to help provide more support
OL,20,Fin mainstream schools.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1771945433
OL,3,CSEND, the disadvantage gap and
OL,4,Cattendance: What's in Labour's plan
OL,5,Cfor schools?
OL,7,FWhile another #1.8bn over the same
OL,8,Fperiod will create a new support
OL,9,Fservice made up of specialists like
OL,10,FSEND teachers and speech and language
OL,11,Ftherapists in every area.
OL,13,FSchools will get #3.7bn of capital
OL,14,Finvestment from last year's Budget to
OL,15,Fcreate spaces away from classrooms
OL,16,Fwhere SEND students can get extra
OL,17,Fhelp. That money will also go towards
OL,18,F60,000 more specialist places in
OL,19,Fmainstream schools.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31811
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1771945433
OL,3,CSEND, the disadvantage gap and
OL,4,Cattendance: What's in Labour's plan
OL,5,Cfor schools?
OL,7,FThe government also announced #200m to
OL,8,Fbetter train teachers in SEND support,
OL,9,Fand schools will be encouraged to join
OL,10,Flocal groupings and work more closely
OL,11,Ftogether on SEND.
OL,13,FShadow education secretary Laura Trott
OL,14,Fargued extra work would come from
OL,15,Fcarrying out individual support plans
OL,16,F(ISPs), branding them a "recipe for
OL,17,Fdisaster".
OL,26,@xD@YOUyD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
