CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1771945433
OL,3,CSEND, the disadvantage gap and
OL,4,Cattendance: What's in Labour's plan
OL,5,Cfor schools?
OL,7,FMeanwhile, Liberal Democrat leader Sir
OL,8,FEd Davey criticised the Tories for
OL,9,Ftheir "failure to apologise for the
OL,10,Fcrisis".JDisadvantage gap and white
OL,11,Fworking-class children falling behind
OL,13,FThe government also announced several
OL,14,Fpolicies to help the most
OL,15,Fdisadvantaged children.
OL,17,FPhillipson said on Monday that
OL,18,F"background shouldn't mean destiny",
OL,19,Finsisting "how a child grows up
OL,20,Fshouldn't dictate where they end up."
OL,26,@qD@GOUrD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
