CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1771945433
OL,3,CSEND, the disadvantage gap and
OL,4,Cattendance: What's in Labour's plan
OL,5,Cfor schools?
OL,7,FShe set a new target to halve the gap
OL,8,Fbetween students from low-income
OL,9,Fbackgrounds and their more affluent
OL,10,Fpeers, pledging "where deprivation is
OL,11,Fdeepest, I will be boldest".
OL,13,FThe government says that if it hits
OL,14,Fthat target, children from low-income
OL,15,Fbackgrounds will achieve around a full
OL,16,Fgrade higher in their GCSEs.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31814
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1771945433
OL,3,CSEND, the disadvantage gap and
OL,4,Cattendance: What's in Labour's plan
OL,5,Cfor schools?
OL,7,FPhillipson announced she will change
OL,8,Fhow funding for disadvantaged students
OL,9,Fis allocated to schools, meaning it
OL,10,Fwill now be based more on how low the
OL,11,Ffamily income is, how long that has
OL,12,Fbeen the case, and where the family
OL,13,Flives, rather than how many children
OL,14,Fare on free school meals.
OL,16,FSchools will be required to join a
OL,17,Ftrust as part of the changes, and
OL,18,Flocal authorities will be given new
OL,19,Fpowers to create trusts.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31815
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1771945433
OL,3,CSEND, the disadvantage gap and
OL,4,Cattendance: What's in Labour's plan
OL,5,Cfor schools?
OL,7,FTrust schools are still funded by the
OL,8,Fgovernment, but are run by charitable
OL,9,Ftrusts, often to help drive school
OL,10,Fimprovement.
OL,12,F"This is an opportunity for schools to
OL,13,Fcome together in new partnerships to
OL,14,Ftake on challenges and bring further
OL,15,Finnovation to the system," the white
OL,16,Fpaper says.
OL,18,FLabour is also launching two new
OL,19,Fschemes to target the most deprived
OL,20,Fstudents, one focused on the North
OL,21,FEast and the other on coastal areas.
OL,26,@tD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31816
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1771945433
OL,3,CSEND, the disadvantage gap and
OL,4,Cattendance: What's in Labour's plan
OL,5,Cfor schools?
OL,7,FBoth projects will also focus
OL,8,Fparticularly on the performance of
OL,9,Fwhite working-class pupils, who have
OL,10,Fsome of the lowest education outcomes.
OL,12,F"We will not tolerate the blind eye
OL,13,Fthat has been turned to the
OL,14,Funderperformance of white working-
OL,15,Fclass children," the government
OL,16,Fdocument says.
OL,18,FNewly-appointed headteachers will also
OL,19,Fbe offered up to #15,000 to work in
OL,20,Fparts of the country where they're
OL,21,F"needed most".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31817
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1771945433
OL,3,CSEND, the disadvantage gap and
OL,4,Cattendance: What's in Labour's plan
OL,5,Cfor schools?
OL,7,FAttendance and 'missing' children
OL,9,FThe government has also set a target
OL,10,Fto improve attendance rates, one of
OL,11,Fthe biggest challenges facing schools
OL,12,Fsince the pandemic.
OL,14,FWhile persistent absence (defined as
OL,15,Fmissing at least 10% of lessons) has
OL,16,Ffallen in the last couple of years,
OL,17,Fsevere absence (missing at least half
OL,18,Fof all lessons) continued to rise. But
OL,19,Fboth figures remain significantly
OL,20,Fhigher than they were pre-Covid.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31818
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1771945433
OL,3,CSEND, the disadvantage gap and
OL,4,Cattendance: What's in Labour's plan
OL,5,Cfor schools?
OL,7,FMinisters have committed to improving
OL,8,Fthe attendance rate by 1.3 percentage
OL,9,Fpoints to over 94%.
OL,11,FThe government is also trying to fix
OL,12,Fwhat it calls the broken "social
OL,13,Fcontract" between schools and
OL,14,Ffamilies, with the white paper aiming
OL,15,Fto make families "believe in education
OL,16,Fonce again".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31819
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1771945433
OL,3,CSEND, the disadvantage gap and
OL,4,Cattendance: What's in Labour's plan
OL,5,Cfor schools?
OL,7,FIt was announced on Monday that the
OL,8,Fgovernment will work with schools,
OL,9,Flocal authorities and families to
OL,10,Fcreate "minimum expectations" from
OL,11,Feach group, to improve relationships
OL,12,Fbetween schools and families.
OL,14,FIt will also send out specialist
OL,15,Fattendance advisers to the areas with
OL,16,Fthe worst attendance rates.
OL,18,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,19,Four political experts are across all
OL,20,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,21,Fto the latest episode below...
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G19/19
